&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibneZHWsor9dA4JenYqRyyaUYVxLZAfrLcLZBf29QX9mmEXlFnoRXeITZuUib5cBouHfHetDpCbia9262UWTia1XRw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1280&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibneZHWsor9dA4JenYqRyyaUYVxLZAfrLcLZBf29QX9mmEXlFnoRXeITZuUib5cBouHfHetDpCbia9262UWTia1XRw/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;558&quot; data-backh=&quot;419&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;顶部的金环可以开合。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibneZHWsor9dA4JenYqRyyaUYVxLZAfrLDL1sMYoNv7QhLp0hqfgpCyHlYUxf9VN226umabRDRMdUbwZUN9oUsg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1280&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.75&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibneZHWsor9dA4JenYqRyyaUYVxLZAfrLDL1sMYoNv7QhLp0hqfgpCyHlYUxf9VN226umabRDRMdUbwZUN9oUsg/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;558&quot; data-backh=&quot;419&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;你也可以把中意的页面取下，粘在记事板上，用来装饰墙面。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibneZHWsor9dA4JenYqRyyaUYVxLZAfrLkJsuGTxALZOjmVficfjzlca2r71tuJVIZepKWmHjTV1qDhDRKJ2532g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;1228&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7198697068403909&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibneZHWsor9dA4JenYqRyyaUYVxLZAfrLkJsuGTxALZOjmVficfjzlca2r71tuJVIZepKWmHjTV1qDhDRKJ2532g/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-backw=&quot;535&quot; data-backh=&quot;385&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;933.6200716845877&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;48.17204301075269&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;1257.0609318996414&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;29.820788530465947&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ibneZHWsor9dA4JenYqRyyaUYVxLZAfrLkwx8un2iciacfLTatNdCV6H20YULE55Qia0QbTa2iaAyI2ftruvhbJr7dA/?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;当你低沉困惑时，请看看那些曾经在地球上发生过的精彩瞬间，也许你会记起杰克·凯鲁亚克所写的那句：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;“我还年轻，我渴望上路。带着最初的激情，追寻着最初的梦想，感受着最初的体验，我们上路吧。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZJp3o7GkkUGv0jES4Ha7GHxibQh9zyRfUcuWq7P7fEcqcZza2xMTK8dQ470oiaBBOdW4nR5ibeATG60KdNdcnibbEQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-w=&quot;900&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.0377777777777777&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
